List of dependencies for Exaile 0.3
===================================

.. note:plugin dependencies should be listed in their description

Dependencies
------------
Essential:

* python (>= 2.5)
* pygst 0.10
* gstreamer-plugins-good 0.10
* mutagen (>= 1.10)
* dbus-python
* pygtk (>= 2.14, built against gtk >= 2.16)
* pygobject (>= 2.18, built with gio support)


Translation:

* gettext

Documentation:

* sphinx

Device detection:

* hal

CD info:

* python-cddb

Scalable icons:

* librsvg2
